**Summary of what was implemented:**

- **`hive completion <shell>`** — new command in `src/commands/completion.ts` that outputs shell completion scripts for **bash**, **zsh**, and **fish**
- **Static completions** for all 12 command names and global flags (`--cwd`, `--version`, `--help`)
- **Dynamic agent name completions** for `launch`, `kill`, `dispatch`, `tail`, and `merge` — resolved at tab-completion time via `hive config --agents --json`
- **Per-command option completions** covering all flags for every command
- **Subcommand completions** for `plan` (11 subcommands) and `templates` (4 subcommands)
- **Installation instructions** shown via `hive completion --help`
- Registered in `src/index.ts` following the standard `registerXxxCommand` pattern

All quality gates pass: typecheck, 122 tests, and build all succeed.
